# VIATOR — Trivy ignore list
#
# Format: one CVE ID per line. Comments start with '#'.
# Add an entry only with a written justification, and re-evaluate
# whenever the base image is bumped.
#
# DO NOT blanket-ignore by severity. The CI workflow already passes
# `--ignore-unfixed` (suppress findings with no upstream fix yet) and
# `--severity CRITICAL,HIGH` (ignore noise below HIGH). Anything fixable
# at HIGH or CRITICAL must be addressed, not silenced here.
